text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">地址：盐城市人民南路66号</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">联系人：张女士</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">联系电话：0515-66696855</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">招标代理机构：江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">地址：盐城市青年西路8号805室</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">联系人：刘工</p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">电话：0515-69057406</p><p><br /></p>','','','','','');
