box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">　一、采购需求</span></span></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><img title=\"1.jpg\" alt=\"1.jpg\" src=\"<!--#p8_attach#-->/cms/item/2024_03/11_15/268fd82ab24d4156.jpg.thumb.jpg\" /></span></span></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">二、遴选报名</span></span></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">　　1.报名资格：</span></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">　　（1）生产厂家或生产厂家委托参与遴选报名的唯一被委托人；</span></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">　　（2）营业执照、医疗器械生产许可证、医疗器械经营许可证、医疗器械注册证等证件齐全且在有效期内。</span></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">　　2.报名方式：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">邮箱报名</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">。</span></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">　　3.报名时间：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">即日起到</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">202</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">4</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">年</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">3</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">月</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">18</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">日</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">24：00前</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">。</span></p><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box;\">　　4.报名所需材料</span