&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">　5.报名</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">邮箱</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">以上报名材料发送至邮箱</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">6</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">遴选</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">时间：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">另行通知</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">检验科项目</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">联系人</span></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">唐</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">老师 &nbsp;联系方式：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">18921892789</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">邮箱：</span><a href=\"mailto:772909836@qq.com\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">772909836@qq.com</span></span></a></p><p style=\"text-indent:32px;line-height:40px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; text-indent: 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; background: r